# NIX ENV
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage user environments (Legacy tool, use nix profile instead).
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix-env -qaP: Search for packages (Legacy).
- nix-env -iA nixpkgs.htop: Install a package.

### Essentials
- nix-env -e htop: Uninstall a package.
- nix-env --list-generations: Show profile history.

## Disclaimers
- Considered legacy. Use 'nix profile' or home-manager for modern setups.

